  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability of USL261 compared
      with that of intranasal (IN) placebo for the treatment of intermittent bouts of increased
      seizure activity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
